1. As an individual, I would like to log in and/or out of the health application(s) each day to allow tracking of my daily weight changes.
2. As an individual, I would like to have the option to save tests and/or records related to my doctor visits for easy access when needed.
3. As an individual, I would like to create reminders for physical activity so I can make an effort to engage in activities that keep me active daily.
4. As an individual, I would like to log the time spent studying versus resting to see if my time management is effective on a daily or weekly basis.
5. As an individual, I would like to track my distance run during workouts to assist in planning for future workouts.
6. As an individual, I would like to log my children's food consumption to ensure that they are getting the proper nutrition.
7. As an individual, I would like to look at a weekly health summary to determine my overall health.
8. As an individual, I would like to set health goals for myself so I have something specific to work towards.
9. As an individual, I would like to use the fitness application without the use of Wi-Fi so I can log my fitness activities regardless of where I am in the world.
10. As an individual, I would like to have easy-to-use buttons or icons to use the health application with little or no assistance.
11. As an individual, I would like to share my health information with friends and family, so they are aware of my health status and can be supportive of my desire to be healthier.
12. As an individual with limited experience, I would like step-by-step guidance on how to maintain a healthy lifestyle through the use of the health application.
